    • Field Detail

      • ISPARSER_binaryFormat

        public static final String ISPARSER_binaryFormat
        Configuration property: Binary input format.
        Property:
        • Name: "InputStreamParser.binaryFormat.s"
        • Data type: BinaryFormat
        • Default: BinaryFormat.HEX
        • Session property: false
        • Methods:
          • InputStreamParserBuilder.binaryFormat(BinaryFormat)
        Description:

        When using the Parser.parse(Object,Class) method on stream-based parsers and the input is a string, this defines the format to use when converting the string into a byte array.

        Example:

        // Create a parser that parses from BASE64. InputStreamParser p = MsgPackParser .create() .binaryFormat(BASE64) .build(); // Same, but use property. InputStreamParser p = MsgPackParser .create() .set(ISPARSER_binaryFormat, "BASE64") .build();

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
